                  Integrate with our P2PWN peer discovery service so that your players can easily create lobbies and join currently active games being hosted.
                </p>
                <p>
                Leverage the P2PWN <a href="./lobby">Lobby gui</a> for live updates of active rooms.
                P2PWN also has a rich API with full control via HTTP REST and websocket requests.
                Review the <a href="https://github.com/Hackbit/nko2018-p2pwithme/wiki/API-Documentation">API documentation here</a>.
                </p>
                <p>
                  The best way to get started is to use one of our reference projects.
